1. *Roditelji* su odgovorni za vaspitanje dece. (Parents are responsible for raising children.)
2. Dete je poslušno odgovaralo *roditeljima*. (The child obediently answered the parents.)
3. *Roditelji* su se nadali da će im se želje ispuniti. (The parents hoped that their wishes would be fulfilled.)
4. *Roditelji* su detetu davali dobre savete. (The parents were giving good advice to the child.)
5. *Roditeljske* ljubavi je bila neponovljiva. (The parental love was irreplaceable.)
6. Oni su poštovali *roditelje*. (They respected their parents.)